sleMplsTpPw.description: This MIB module containg the managed object definition for MPLS-TP pseudowire(PW) operation. copyright (c) 2015 Dasan Networks and the persons identified as authors of the code. All rights reserved.

sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoTable.name: sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoTable
sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoTable.description: This table specifies information for configuring and status monitoring that is common to all service types and PSN types.

sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoEntry.name: sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoEntry
sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoEntry.description: A row in this table is indexed by sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoId.

sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoName.name: sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoName
sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoName.description: PW Virtual Circuit Name. It identifies an entry on this table.

sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoOwner.name: sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoOwner
sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoOwner.description: Use to indentify the owner of the PW.

sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoSvlanId.name: sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoSvlanId
sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoSvlanId.description: PW SVlan. This should be a valid VLAN-ID when sleMplsTpPwCfgOperMode is pwTaggedMode(2).

sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoPwStatus.name: sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoPwStatus
sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoPwStatus.description: This object is used to set the pw status tlv.

sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoVcStitchName.name: sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoVcStitchName
sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoVcStitchName.description: Multi-segment PW FIB entry stitch name.

sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoPriority.name: sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoPriority
sleMplsTpPwCfgInfoPriority.description: PW Priority. In MPLS-TP case, primary only supported.

sleMplsTpPwCfgControlRequest.name: sleMplsTpPwCfgControlRequest
sleMplsTpPwCfgControlRequest.description: This object holds the possible read-write columns that can be modified in the Pw table. For each read-write column of Pw table, a Set Operation control value is added in this object.

sleMplsTpPwCfgControlStatus.name: sleMplsTpPwCfgControlStatus
sleMplsTpPwCfgControlStatus.description: This object displays the status of the configuration done.

sleMplsTpPwCfgControlTimer.name: sleMplsTpPwCfgControlTimer
sleMplsTpPwCfgControlTimer.description: This object is based on the SLE style where a timer is configured for every control table.

sleMplsTpPwCfgControlTimestamp.name: sleMplsTpPwCfgControlTimestamp
sleMplsTpPwCfgControlTimestamp.description: This object specifies the time at which the configuration is done.

sleMplsTpPwCfgControlReqResult.name: sleMplsTpPwCfgControlReqResult
sleMplsTpPwCfgControlReqResult.description: The standard result of the SET operation is stored here.

sleMplsTpPwCfgControlName.name: sleMplsTpPwCfgControlName
sleMplsTpPwCfgControlName.description: PW Virtual Circuit Name. It identifies an entry on this table.

sleMplsTpPwCfgControlOwner.name: sleMplsTpPwCfgControlOwner
sleMplsTpPwCfgControlOwner.description: Use to indentify the owner of the PW.

sleMplsTpPwCfgControlSvlanId.name: sleMplsTpPwCfgControlSvlanId
sleMplsTpPwCfgControlSvlanId.description: PW SVlan. This should be a valid VLAN-ID when sleMplsTpPwCfgOperMode is pwTaggedMode(2).

sleMplsTpPwCfgControlVcStitchName.name: sleMplsTpPwCfgControlVcStitchName
sleMplsTpPwCfgControlVcStitchName.description: Multi-segmen PW FIB Entry stitch name.
